    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Miracle In Bilbao</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Rose Cividanes calls Frank Gehry's new Guggenheim Museum in Bilbao, Spain, a monstrosity (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The negative introduction to the city of Bilbao (bleak, rusty, bomb scares) leaves me to wonder why it was chosen for this ''miracle.'' Can it be that no one else wanted this monstrosity?</p>
        <p>Rose Cividanes  Hackensack, N.J.</p>
      </block>
